Text: SJUKT bra album! hoppus kan verkligen göra musik

Plus 44... Nice!

Mark Hoppus and Travis Barker from Blink 182 making music together again, it's great (with their friends Craig and Shane, both on guitar)!

The sound is not far from Blink 182 or Boxcar Racer..
Underbart!!! Väntat länge på denna. Travis e grym! Älskar honom på trummorna!

One song is missing, "Baby, Come On(Acoustic).

You didn't happen to download this from iTunes, did you?
